ActIndian Act
SubjectMoosomin Indian Reserve No. 112S, Saskatchewan - Easement
PrecisOrder (a) consenting to the exercise by SASKATCHEWAN TELECOMMUNICATIONS of the power to take an interest in certain lands within MOOSOMIN INDIAN RESERVE RESERVE No. 112S, in Saskatchewan; and (b) granting the company the required easement.
